message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL. This is because the paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques, which are commonly studied in these sub-categories. Specifically, the paper proposes a question answering system that uses neural-network ranking models to select a sentence from a product description in an online marketplace. This involves encoding strategies such as recurrent neural networks and feed-forward attention layers, which are commonly used in NLP and machine learning research.
